high_descs: Walk to the kitchen table with the coffee maker on it.
Grab lettuce off the kitchen table.
Walk to the front of the fridge on your left.
Put lettuce in the fridge, then grab it.
Walk to the kitchen counter between the stove and fridge.
Put the lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Chill lettuce and prepare it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the left of the coffee maker.
Pick up the head of lettuce to the right of the tomato.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the lettuce on the top shelf of the fridge, close the door, open the door, take the lettuce out of the fridge, and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the head of lettuce on the counter in front of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: To chill lettuce and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and then left. Find the long counter to the right.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter, to the right.
Hold the lettuce and turn to the left, a small amount, and move to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce inside. Shut the fridge and then open it again. Take the lettuce out and shut the door.
Hold the lettuce and take a few steps to the left.
Place the lettuce on the counter, in front of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Chill lettuce and place it on the counter.
